elilong: elilong (UEFI Boot Manager)
elilong:
elilong: elilong is a lightweight UEFI bootloader for Linux. It provides a
elilong: simple boot menu, supports multiple kernel configurations, and
elilong: automates the synchronization of kernels and initrds to the EFI
elilong: System Partition (ESP).
elilong:
elilong: It is designed to be a modern, easy-to-understand alternative to
elilong: older UEFI loaders.
